data.description: [Seller Incentive! Offering $3k flex cash + Washer/Dryer package within accepted list price offer prior to end of January] Brand NEW Construction in the Murray Hill area, about an half mile from all of the popular Murray Hill spots! 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home with an open floor plan. Kitchen includes new fridge and range oven. Durable, wood-look vinyl flooring throughout the interior, with cementious hardi board siding on the exterior. New Roof, New AC, New Plumbing, New Electric, brand New home!! Schedule a private tour today. **including Builder Warranty**[Unlock Your Dream Home with Up to $10,000 in Down Payment / Closing Cost Assistance! Give us a call for more details to see if you qualify.] (Photos are of similar floorplan, but not exact home, some finishes may slightly differ)
